    "description_long": "This is a compact hatchback car with a teal blue exterior and a streamlined, modern design. The vehicle features two side doors and a rear hatch door, with black-tinted windows and white-rimmed tires. The headlights and taillights are integrated smoothly into the body, and the car has subtle chrome detailing along the sides. The front and rear bumpers are slightly rounded, and the car sits low to the ground, emphasizing its urban-friendly proportions. The license plates are visible on both the front and rear, and the overall build suggests a lightweight, efficient city vehicle.",
